title: 820-3476 - RAM Beep after short in Q7430
message:
Logic board with no history. But perfect, without oxidation.

There was a short on the PPBus because of the Q7430. Replaced it, board turned on again, but with RAM beeping.

I have 1.35v on PP1V35_S3, but when I test it off, it shows as a short (023.1), in 0.040 diode mode.

I compared it with another board, diode mode is 0.110 and there is no short on this line.

title: 820-3476 - RAM Beep after short in Q7430
message: RAM chips, or CPU damaged by overvoltage through Q7430.

title: 820-3476 - RAM Beep after short in Q7430
message: I imagined! Thank you very much!
